title: 2016 United States presidential election in Ohio
added: The shift from 2012 and the fact that Trump won Ohio by a comfortable 8 point margin left Ohio's status as a bellwether uncertain and Ohio would go on to lose it's bellwether status four years later, Voting for Trump while Biden won the presidency.
